}
```

### 0.4 Execution Environments

| Environment                      | Role                                                         |
| -------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| Node.js 20 LTS (PC)              | This module — all subcomponents                              |
| Browser / PWA (iPhone)           | Sends SDP/ICE, streams live preview, records + uploads video |
